{"title":"雷锋，在今天","authors":["白隼"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋，在今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白隼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要你来了，只要你在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年到头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是宜于播种的时候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们熟悉你的笑容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热切盼望春燕如期归来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实你并没有离开我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些年，一直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"置身于共和国大步行进的队列。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是烟雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一度迷蒙你的身影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绚烂的花丛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾被沾湿的泥水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄得斑斑驳驳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱的河流终要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向指定的地域。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们笑着迎接你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也请你接纳我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作你亲爱的弟兄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们站在地球顶端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听远方纷乱的脚步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐逼近烽火台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你像一丛奋然开放的鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滤净空气中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分贝过量的噪音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们每天都得接受你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微笑的询问。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白荷世界容不下一点灰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟你在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会变成火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会变成钢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者晶莹的露珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在神州大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静闪亮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}